Reasons which can fail a deployment
====================================
Insufficient quota
Readiness probe failures
Image pull errors
Insufficient permissions
Limit ranges
Application runtime misconfiguration


if the duration of deployment exceeds the progress deadline seconds than it will consider the deployment as stalled.







